## 9. Build Notes
- Reuse existing Opportunity action UX pattern used for premium/indemnity edits.
- Keep defaults configuration-driven so NB and MTA values can differ.
- Ensure both submission entry paths call the same NB Fee__c creation service.
- Keep cancellation/cancel-reissue behavior aligned with current enterprise processing in this phase.
 
 
